type.description:
### ⚠️ Requires [Apugli](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) to be installed! ⚠️

## Action On Equip

---


[Power Type](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/action_on_equip).

Executes an action when an item is equipped.

Type ID: `apugli:action_on_equip`

---

### Example
```json
{
    "type": "apugli:action_on_equip",
    "head": {
        "type": "apoli:ingredient",
        "ingredient": {
            "item": "minecraft:netherite_helmet"
        }
    },
    "action": {
        "type": "apoli:heal",
        "amount": 6
    }
}
```
This power heals you for 3 hearts when you equip a netherite helmet.

